pageContext.claim: “Whatever happened to the so-called ‘informer’ to Whistleblower #1? Seems to have disappeared after I released the Transcript of the call. Shouldn't he be on the list to testify? Witch Hunt!”
pageContext.analysis: This claim makes little sense, as the whistleblower in his complaint mentioned multiple U.S. officials. Several diplomats and Trump administration officials corroborated the whistleblower's account.
